# Chartoon Networth Frontend Environment Variables

# URL of the backend API
# In local development, you can leave this empty or commented out so Vite uses the local proxy.
# If testing the production build locally or using a specific backend instance, uncomment and set one of the following:

# Local Backend (default proxy target)
# VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:5000/api

# Azure Production Backend
# VITE_API_URL=https://chartoon-networth-agfwgvapa9aaesgk.canadacentral-01.azurewebsites.net/api
